metadata.name: Surrealestate 1
metadata.description: Settler Surrealestate Land Plots - The perfect place for your new life. Surrealestates are a collection of NFT with a max supply of 10,000. Stretching across worlds and galaxies, what could be more enticing than the hope of a new home? A new life? the galactic dream. Built from an amalgamation of materials and designed by deciphering Earth's own transmissions, the Surrealestates are ready to purchase.
